{
  "stem": "802.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- the-- the-- generally, the-- the people were chased.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to run.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had these knapsacks, which was an indication of our undying optimism, because we didn't know what-- what-- what would happen to us ultimately.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And finally, we got to this-- this no man's land, which I described before-- the four camps that were adjacent to each other, four camps for men, and one for women.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And between those there was a kind of limbo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There we stayed another few days, I think about three.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Three was the magic number.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It always is the magic number for good things, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and we were starving.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't have any food in the train either.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we-- my father and I drank water from the puddles, you know, the rain puddles.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we were separated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Men and women were separated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father was taken to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we were told from a distance, a week or so later, men and women were separated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But when we worked, we walked-- actually, there was no work in Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'll explain it in a moment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We-- we marched in groups.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so once, a man screamed to us, your father was killed, so we knew.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were in close proximity to each other, so it was not a great distance.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, we-- we kept on asking, do you know what happened to this one?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do you know what happened to that one?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they told us that my father was killed in the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I often, till this day-- and I guess as I'm growing old, it-- it becomes-- the vision is more immediate.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
